org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.api

Interface StatisticBinningStrategy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinningStrategy, Persistable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompositeBinningStrategy, DataTypeBinningStrategy, FieldValueBinningStrategy, NumericRangeFieldValueBinningStrategy, PartitionBinningStrategy, SpatialFieldValueBinningStrategy, TimeRangeFieldValueBinningStrategy

    public interface StatisticBinningStrategy
extends Persistable, BinningStrategy
    Base interface for statistic binning strategies. These strategies allow a statistic's values to be split up by an arbitrary strategy. This allows a simple statistic to be used in many different ways.
